column5: I am heading up to Minaki next week with the family to do some walleye fishing. It will be the first time in Canada for some of us. Does anyone have a recent report or tips for what is working up there now? Any help is appreciated. Thanks!
Looks like jig and minnow on the points and eddies are working. I can tell you that there is a buttload of fisherman and boats running the system. Very heavy traffic.
